1542
01:31:57.370 --> 01:32:00.630
So this data suggested that the G12C inhibitor actually

1543
01:32:00.790 --> 01:32:04.050
sways away the cell from aurora kinase A-induced

1544
01:32:04.110 --> 01:32:07.130
