1545
01:32:07.170 --> 01:32:10.724
catastrophe.But how do GTOX

1546
01:32:10.954 --> 01:32:12.634
inhibitor determine that cell fate?

1547
01:32:13.314 --> 01:32:17.114
Well, the established theory has suggested that

1548
01:32:17.494 --> 01:32:21.114
for a mitotic cell to determine its cell fate, it's

1549
01:32:21.734 --> 01:32:25.634
determined by a balance of the cyclin B1 dynamics and the

1550
01:32:25.754 --> 01:32:29.674
death signal. So rapid degradation of cyclin B1 will cause

1551
01:32:29.694 --> 01:32:33.654
cells to slip or divide, and the slow degradation of cyclin B1

1552
01:32:33.694 --> 01:32:36.294
will cause cell to undergo catastrophe.

1553
01:32:37.954 --> 01:32:38.114
So,

1554
01:32:39.634 --> 01:32:43.414
consistent with that theory, we have shown that GTOX inhibitor-treated cell

1555
01:32:43.454 --> 01:32:47.114
have elevated cyclin B1 level at the onset of

1556
01:32:49.574 --> 01:32:53.274
mitosis, and this progress through the entire mitosis,

1557
01:32:54.134 --> 01:32:57.654
while the proapoptotic protein BIM

1558
01:32:58.054 --> 01:32:59.414
not have any difference.

1559
01:33:00.954 --> 01:33:04.454
And then we ask, how does GTOX inhibitor stabilize the cyclin

1560
01:33:04.514 --> 01:33:08.294
B1? So, in fact, the DNA

1561
01:33:08.374 --> 01:33:10.954
damage during mitosis can activate

1562
01:33:11.814 --> 01:33:15.374
DNA repair pathway ATR and CHEK1, which may

1563
01:33:15.474 --> 01:33:19.034
stabilize the cyclin B1 through APCC cofactor

1564
01:33:19.134 --> 01:33:19.894
CDH1.

1565
01:33:20.714 --> 01:33:24.534
To test whether ATM, ATR, DNA repair pathway

1566
01:33:24.854 --> 01:33:28.494
contribute to our phenotype, we knock ATM, ATR down

1567
01:33:28.854 --> 01:33:32.814
and notice that that can completely reverse the cell death phenotype

1568
01:33:33.074 --> 01:33:34.574
bring out by the combination.

1569
01:33:35.834 --> 01:33:39.794
And the cells with ATR knockdown can also reduce the cyclin B1

1570
01:33:40.694 --> 01:33:44.174
accumulation induced by KRAS GTOX inhibitor.

1571
01:33:44.954 --> 01:33:48.914
And the cell with deficient ATR can also

1572
01:33:48.974 --> 01:33:52.594
