1573
01:33:52.634 --> 01:33:56.524
GTOX-induced mitotic slowing as well as aura kinase

1574
01:33:56.594 --> 01:33:58.314
A-induced mitotic arrest.

1575
01:33:59.594 --> 01:34:03.494
When we isolate the mitotic fraction of the micronuclei

1576
01:34:03.594 --> 01:34:07.454
